    {
      "key": "ed916621-66d6-41bb-82ce-aa7b29536481",
      "position": 5,
      "properties": {
        "description": "*Check For Understanding Question(s) and solutions can be found in each lesson on Code Studio. These questions can be used for an exit ticket.*",
        "name": "Assessment: Check for Understanding",
        "progression_name": "Check for Understanding"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "ed916621-66d6-41bb-82ce-aa7b29536481",
        "lesson_activity.key": "86614414-01a1-48a3-a8a4-7f390d0acc45"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "7f88c073-713e-45d1-8b7d-4b7f4be7be54",
      "position": 1,
      "properties": {
        "description": "Before working towards the next benchmark, it is helpful to assess your achievement of this benchmark and to get feedback on your ideas and planning.",
        "name": "Peer Review and Feedback",
        "remarks": true
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "7f88c073-713e-45d1-8b7d-4b7f4be7be54",
        "lesson_activity.key": "ee2784af-331f-4d47-83f1-5fbc505a1f67"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "cbb01ba1-be58-4e8e-a150-b223f765b21f",
      "position": 2,
      "properties": {
        "description": "**Group:** Place students in pairs.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Distribute:** Give a copy of the Project Planning Feedback handout to each student.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Review the feedback process.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Have students identify a question to frame the feedback session.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Have students ask their framing questions and share feedback. Students should take notes on their Project Planning Feedback handout.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Have students individually respond to the prompts on their Project Planning Feedback, identify the user stories that will make up their second benchmark, and post tasks they want to complete for the second benchmark in the \"To Do\" column of their Project Planning Board."
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "cbb01ba1-be58-4e8e-a150-b223f765b21f",
        "lesson_activity.key": "ee2784af-331f-4d47-83f1-5fbc505a1f67"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "2e2f91b7-6adf-47cf-a130-59abc22f1975",
      "position": 1,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Introduce the lesson objectives.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Introduce the Question of the Day.",
        "duration": "15",
        "name": "AI-Generated Art"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "2e2f91b7-6adf-47cf-a130-59abc22f1975",
        "lesson_activity.key": "26879553-c5f0-47cd-896e-39c5cbea1e18"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "10ae3607-9d3d-4fd8-8b37-1cfd8a38236e",
      "position": 2,
      "properties": {
        "description": "We previously explored image manipulation and how machine learning can be used to create deep fakes. Today, we'll take a look at another way AI and machine learning is used to generate images.",
        "remarks": true
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "10ae3607-9d3d-4fd8-8b37-1cfd8a38236e",
        "lesson_activity.key": "26879553-c5f0-47cd-896e-39c5cbea1e18"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "b1f7b849-f9e1-42df-a0d7-9fa657eaa7e3",
      "position": 3,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Introduce the example of AI-generated artwork.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Discuss:** *What does this make you wonder or feel?*\n\n**Discussion Goal:** Students share their reactions to the example and discuss their thoughts on whether they believe this was right or ethical. Students may express surprise or may agree with the person who won the award.",
        "tips": [
          {
            "type": "teachingTip",
            "markdown": "Use the Retrieve-Pair-Share strategy to facilitate this discussion by directing students to write down their thoughts and ideas first, then pair up students to compare their answers and expand their notes. This allows time for individual processing and idea generation before sharing thoughts with others. Ask students to share the ideas they discussed with their partners as a class."
          }
        ]
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "b1f7b849-f9e1-42df-a0d7-9fa657eaa7e3",
        "lesson_activity.key": "26879553-c5f0-47cd-896e-39c5cbea1e18"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "95970110-3acf-46d8-b5e2-30a40986eb61",
      "position": 4,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Show examples of AI art-generating programs.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Click through the animated slide to explain how AI art-generating programs work."
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "95970110-3acf-46d8-b5e2-30a40986eb61",
        "lesson_activity.key": "26879553-c5f0-47cd-896e-39c5cbea1e18"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "76d49042-f913-42e8-a6b2-92ff864d1bfb",
      "position": 5,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Discuss:** *Should we consider AI-generated images art?*\n\n**Discussion Goal:** Students share their opinions on whether AI-generated images can be considered art and explain their reasoning. For example, some students might believe that these are not art because of the lack of human effort while other students might believe these are art because the images have to be generated with prompts and modifications to achieve the desired effect."
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "76d49042-f913-42e8-a6b2-92ff864d1bfb",
        "lesson_activity.key": "26879553-c5f0-47cd-896e-39c5cbea1e18"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "fcb7a662-298f-47cc-8e5a-383e140b44f6",
      "position": 6,
      "properties": {
        "description": "Programs that generate images use large amounts of data to train the AI. This data often consists of images found on the web from other artists and may be used without their knowledge or consent.",
        "duration": "15",
        "name": "Intellectual Property",
        "remarks": true
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "fcb7a662-298f-47cc-8e5a-383e140b44f6",
        "lesson_activity.key": "26879553-c5f0-47cd-896e-39c5cbea1e18"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "c01c576e-2312-449d-90a4-96f81284285a",
      "position": 7,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Define ***intellectual property***.\n\n**Group:** Place students in small groups of three or four.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Distribute:** Give each group a different colored pen or marker.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Explain the instructions for the AI Carousel and assign each group to a station.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Give groups 1-2 minutes to discuss the topic or question at their station and write down their thoughts and ideas on the chart paper using their assigned colored pen or marker.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Direct students to rotate to the next station and read the new topic or question and the previous group's responses. Have students discuss the topic or question and the responses with their group and add new thoughts and ideas to the chart paper using their assigned colored pen or marker. Students can also write questions about things the other groups wrote. Continue this process until each group is back at their original station.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Have each group share the responses at their station."
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "c01c576e-2312-449d-90a4-96f81284285a",
        "lesson_activity.key": "26879553-c5f0-47cd-896e-39c5cbea1e18"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "ad76d12b-801e-46dd-a538-f5590232e169",
      "position": 1,
      "properties": {
        "description": "AI-generated images can be useful in some scenarios, but there are some ethical and legal concerns that we have seen that should be considered in how we create and use these images.",
        "name": "But, Because, So",
        "remarks": true
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "ad76d12b-801e-46dd-a538-f5590232e169",
        "lesson_activity.key": "0d1c25c6-f605-4c39-88e9-3268a6c91135"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "90b9a44f-bc84-4873-ae55-3594dc712427",
      "position": 2,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Direct students to respond to the prompt.",
        "tips": [
          {
            "type": "teachingTip",
            "markdown": "If time permits, have students share their responses with a neighbor or as a class."
          }
        ]
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "90b9a44f-bc84-4873-ae55-3594dc712427",
        "lesson_activity.key": "0d1c25c6-f605-4c39-88e9-3268a6c91135"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "6753658a-3dd6-4c7b-bc74-9e65eec51a46",
      "position": 3,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Review the concepts covered in this lesson.\n\n<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Do This:** Review the Question of the Day.",
        "tips": [
          {
            "type": "teachingTip",
            "markdown": "The Unit 7 Guide includes the Question of the Day and an end-of-lesson reflection prompt for students to summarize what they have learned and reflect on their progress. Have students respond to these prompts after reviewing the concepts covered in this lesson to help them process and make meaningful connections with the new content."
          }
        ]
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "6753658a-3dd6-4c7b-bc74-9e65eec51a46",
        "lesson_activity.key": "0d1c25c6-f605-4c39-88e9-3268a6c91135"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "d8f5452e-28be-451f-a360-1749fc4c71bb",
      "position": 4,
      "properties": {
        "description": "<i class=\"fa fa-list-alt\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Display:** Key Vocabulary"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "d8f5452e-28be-451f-a360-1749fc4c71bb",
        "lesson_activity.key": "0d1c25c6-f605-4c39-88e9-3268a6c91135"
      }
    },
    {
      "key": "4c270c71-09b5-4a40-9a55-e0cac00116ff",
      "position": 5,
      "properties": {
        "description": "---"
      },
      "seeding_key": {
        "activity_section.key": "4c270c71-09b5-4a40-9a55-e0cac00116ff",
